message.content:
Breakfast: Scrambled eggs with spinach and tomatoes, whole grain toast.
Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, bell peppers, olives, feta cheese, and a light vinaigrette dressing.
Dinner: Baked salmon with lemon and dill served over quinoa with steamed broccoli on the side.
Snack: Handful of almonds or other nuts/seeds, along with an apple or banana.
